</P>
<P>
   With SMU (21-9) ahead 23-21 with 10:12 left in the first half,
the Mustangs failed to scored on their next seven possessions while
Southwest Missouri ran off 11 straight points in taking a 43-31
halftime lead.
</P>
<P>
   SMU narrowed the margin to 48-42 with 16:58 remaining before
Southwest Missouri opened a 13-0 run to go up 61-42 with 14:12
left.
</P>
<P>
   Brakebill controlled the second half, scoring 13 points and
grabbing eight rebounds.
</P>
<P>
   The Mustangs shot just 34 percent from the floor, including
5-of-28 on 3-pointers, and 52 percent from the line.
</P>
<P>
