hardcover books during the week ended last Saturday at more than
2,500 B. Dalton, Barnes &AMP; Noble, Bookland, Books-a-Million, Books &AMP;
Co., Bookstar, Bookstop, Borders, Brentano's, Coles, Coopersmith,
Crown, Doubleday, Scribners, Super Crown and Waldenbooks stores, as
well as sales from online retailers barnesandnoble.com and
Amazon.com.
