   White House: www.whitehouse.gov
</P>
<P>
   Department of Housing and Urban Development:
www.hud.gov/news.html
</P>
<P>
   National Shooting Sports Foundation: www.nssf.org
</P>
<P>
   Smith &AMP; Wesson: www.smith-wesson.com
</P>
