Chenowith 4-8 2-2 10, Earl 1-2 1-2 3, London 0-0 0-0 0. Totals
34-60 10-21 81.
</P>
<P>
   Halftime score--DePaul 33, Kansas 32. End of regulation: DePaul
70, Kansas 70. 3-Point Goals--DePaul 6-19 (Richardson 3-9, Simmons
2-6, Burno 1-2, McPherson 0-1, Tulley 0-1), Kansas 3-9 (Hinrich
2-2, Boschee 1-6, Bradford 0-1). Fouled out--Simmons, Hinrich.
